{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9477f7b770","title":"给于学忠“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"41287350a8","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":22,"articleId":"9477f7b770"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01e91ff253","type":"paragraph","text":"给于学忠“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"983a8580d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月22日）于主席勋鉴：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"77de6b669d","type":"paragraph","text":"两军相处密迩，未能通候，甚以为歉。凤稳先生热诚爱国，对日抗战早具同心，而西北停战议和，首先贵我两军停止自相残杀，实为刻不容缓。兹派彭雨峰君晋误崇阶，申述散方联合救国之旨，敬析不传赐教，指示一切。抗日合作成功之日，两军之利，抑亦民族国家之福也。专此","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"ea17242bbf","type":"paragraph","text":"即颂勋祺。不一。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"bd27f46738","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"a23f2a20b8","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十二日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"d2837922d5","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]于学忠（1890—1964），山东蓬莱人，当时任国民党甘肃省政府主席、国民党军第五十一军军长。新中国成立后，曾任国防委员会委员。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"},{"id":"c485a0d294","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]彭雨峰，即彭雪枫，当时是中国共产党派往山西等地做统一战线工作的代表。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770"}],"page":{"id":"a641790e07","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"9477f7b770","start":161,"end":161}}}},"__N_SSG":true}